name: Big Softie, 2020
description:
Big Softie, 2020
Smoke, acrylic, spray paint and ink on canvas

This piece of art is made from acrylic, spray paint, and ink on canvas. The goal was to create something that would make you feel like hugging the canvas. Gigantic and plush looking “BIG SOFTIE” comes to life just begging you to give him a squeeze.

Artist: Muka
Original: https://www.artsy.net/artwork/muka-big-softie
https://artbymuka.com
